      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:25:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可突破 10,000 美元纪录，巧克力价格也随之上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/cocoa-soars-past-10-000-pummeling-chocolate-and-candy-makers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，可可期货飙升至每吨前所未有的 10,000 美元上方，随后回吐涨幅，并从今年主要巧克力原料价格翻倍的历史性上涨中稍作喘息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/cocoa-soars-past-10-000-pummeling-chocolate-and-candy-makers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 10:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
